Class Logman

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.canarymod.logger.Logman

  • public class Logman
extends java.lang.Object
    CanaryMod Log manager.

    You can get an appropriate logger for your plugin here.

    Author:
    Chris (damagefilter), Jos Kuijpers, Jason (darkdiplomat), Larry1123 Updated to make use of log4j
